\end{equation}

\end_inset

因为
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{a}(x_{1},y_{1},z_{1})$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{b}(x_{2},y_{2},z_{2})$
\end_inset

